# artifacts/ui-screenshots/.gitignore
#
# Keep:
#   diff-report.json — last recorded diff scores (small, useful to track)
#
# Ignore (large binary artifacts generated per-run):
#   baseline/  — copies of mockup PNGs from docs/mockups-v3/images/ (re-generated by ui:baseline)
#   current/   — screenshots captured each CI run (uploaded as CI artifacts)
#   diff/      — diff images generated each CI run (uploaded as CI artifacts)
baseline/
current/
diff/
